## Local runtime

Use `ldev` as the official local entrypoint:

```bash
ldev doctor
ldev setup
ldev start
ldev status
ldev logs --since 5m --no-follow
ldev stop
```

Useful namespaces:

```bash
ldev deploy --help
ldev osgi --help
ldev liferay --help
ldev worktree --help
```

